Hearo - A Hardware musicplayer for Spotify


Edit Systemd entries:
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/hearo-event-daemon.service


Start Daemons:
sudo systemctl start hearo-event-daemon
sudo systemctl start hearo-buttons-listener.service

Stop Daemons:
sudo systemctl stop hearo-event-daemon
sudo systemctl stop hearo-buttons-listener.service